All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, Iterable<T>, Collection<T>, Set<T>
public class BetterSet<T>
extends HashSet<T>

A parameterized class that supports specific operation on sets of objects. It is organized to extend the Java HashSet class and it implements intersection, subset, and superset operations.
